            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://movie.douban.com/review/3090173/">从此萧郎是路人</a></h2>

                <div id="review_3090173_short" class="review-short" data-rid="3090173">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        几年前我一直在思考一个问题，到底是周星驰成就了香港喜剧，还是王晶、刘镇伟、李力持、黄百鸣、谷德昭、吴孟达、田启文等一众幕后英雄成就了周星驰？后来我想通了，离开了王晶、刘镇伟、李力持、吴孟达这些人，周星驰依然是周星驰，依然有无可匹敌的号召力；可离开了周星驰，...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3090173-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_3090173_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_3090173_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="3090173" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-3090173">
                                119
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn down" data-rid="3090173" title="没用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/68849027911140623cf338c9845893c4566db851/pics/down.png" />
                        <span id="r-useless_count-3090173">
                                14
                        </span>
